  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink79-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">taṉṉoṭu kūṭātu taṉittup puṉalāṭukiṉṟāṉ eṉak kēṭṭut talainiṉṟu
          oḻukappaṭṭāniṉṟa parattai tāṉum taṉiyē pōyp puṉalāṭiṉāḷāka avaḷai ūṭal tīrttaṟ poruṭṭākat
          talaimakaṉ ceṉṟu tāṉ aṟiyāṉ pōla nakaiyāṭik kūṟik kaippaṟṟiyavaḻi avaḷ tōḻi colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink79">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>putuppuṉa lāṭi yamartta kaṇṇaḷ</l>
          <l>yārmaka ḷivaḷeṉap paṟṟiya makiḻna</l>
          <l>yārmaka ḷāyiṉu maṟiyāy</l>
          <l>nīyār makaṉaiyem paṟṟi yōyē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

<l>           O delightful man! </l> 
<l>           You who grabbed hold of her and asked, </l> 
<l rend="indent4">             'Whose daughter is this, </l> 
<l>           She with the beligerent eyes, </l> 
<l>           bathing in the new floods?' –  </l> 
<l>           You will [never] find out whose daughter she is. </l> 
<l>           And just whose son are you, to be grabbing hold of us like this?' </l> 

          
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
